lc command

    (A)  FUNCTION
         Lc command reports on specified facility with its type and
         name.

    (B)  SYNOPSIS

         lc [ { <facility> } ]

    (C)  PARAMETERS
         <facility>
           specifies the facility to report on, which is regarded as
           the one at current postion if not specified.

    (D)  NOTES
         If the <facility> is not a leaf, this command also reports on
         its children.

    (E)  SEE ALSO
         lcn command
